3611,"uid":46120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T05:45:20.000Z","msg":"美國應該同台灣簽台美共同防禦極權條約。台灣公民除了廢佬，新一代應該唔會反對美軍駐守。左岸一定又嘈又演習又話要出兵，咁就將出兵主動權俾佢<br />\n<br />\nTrump 年代已經睇到，放兩艘航母係度。將出兵主動權讓俾極權，極權係會hang機當無事發生。<br />\n<br />\n美軍登陸台灣之時就係「武統」之日<br />\n環時：美軍坐飛機降落，唔計<br />\n人民日報：美軍上岸、上岸唔係登陸，唔計。"},{"pid":"affa3ed760d1445d24acc01a041a8a505ff723fd","tid":2433611,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T05:48:24.000Z","msg":"其實早日解決咪唔使年年燒軍費囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732b0208b8e95f4b3c78ea2730cee6a0b2896f3f","tid":2433611,"uid":213812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T05:49:01.000Z","msg":"All talk...."},{"pid":"f4b3ed8fbd1fd352630b6ebac439f6f3c6fb1332","tid":2433611,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T05:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0469f7416430ba8729ca26a18ff73628739c8e5a","tid":2433611,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T09:26:50.000Z","msg":"導彈基地瞄準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順手瞄準"},{"pid":"9d2e5f3ded55803a351675b6c4685520f845b246","tid":2433611,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"affa3ed760d1445d24acc01a041a8a505ff723fd","tid":2433611,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T05:48:24.000Z","msg":"其實早日解決咪唔使年年燒軍費囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T09:27:42.000Z","msg":"核平中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101ba74e5440dc42f089070d9f0db9f174a5f7ca","tid":2433611,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T09:48:20.000Z","m